These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, november, july
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, dressmaker, analyst
1. the dressmaker is the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the analyst and the person who's birthday is in november##2
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Birthday      | november | july | may |
| Job   | dressmaker     | musician    | analyst   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, grapefruit, grapes
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, dutch, american
1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
2. the american is between the spanish and the person eating avocado##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Food   | avocado    | grapes        | grapefruit |
| Nationality     | dutch | american | spanish         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, thai
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, may, november
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the canadian is between the person who's birthday is in may and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Nationality   | malaysian | canadian     | thai |
| Birthday        | may  | november | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, mango, artichoke
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, september
1. the person eating pear is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person eating artichoke is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Food   | mango  | artichoke     | pear |
| Birthday           | may | september | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, purple, azure
There 3 different types of food: avocado, lemon, zucchini
1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating avocado is between the person eating zucchini and the person eating lemon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Color   | purple | azure     | ivory |
| Food     | zucchini    | avocado | lemon    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, dog, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, tram
1. the person driving the helicopter is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the snake##2
2. the owner of the snake is the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Pet   | snake  | dog   | rat        |
| Transport         | roller | helicopter | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, october, august
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, camping, gardening
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Birthday          | october  | september  | august |
| Hobby   | camping | dancing | gardening     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, september, june
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, paramedic, doctor
1. the person who's birthday is in september is the doctor##1
2. the paramedic is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | june   | july  | september  |
| Job   | nurse | paramedic | doctor |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, fonseca, havana
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, french, russian
1. the malaysian is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the malaysian is between the havana-smoker and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Cigar       | havana | oliveros | fonseca  |
| Nationality   | russian    | malaysian        | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
House: cottage, colonial, futuristic
City: edinburgh, paris, miami
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the colonial house is between the person traveling to miami and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| House         | futuristic | colonial | cottage |
| City   | miami     | edinburgh    | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig, rabbit
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, van, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person driving the skateboard##2
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | lizard      | rabbit      |
| Transport       | van  | snowmobile | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, coral
City: hamburg, marseilles, new-york
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to marseilles##2
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Color   | lavender | fuchsia   | coral   |
| City         | marseilles | new-york | hamburg |

