.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, filmmaking, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | soy-milk | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby     | filmmaking    | puzzles    | dancing |

