1. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the swisher-smoker is between the person who likes fuchsia and the baccarat-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Color   | fuchsia  | apricot   | grey  |
| Cigar        | siglo | swisher | baccarat |

