.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, red, emerald
There 3 different types of food: corn, lime, broccoli
1. the person eating corn is between the person who likes red and the person who likes emerald##2
2. the person who likes red is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes red is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Color   | red | blue   | emerald   |
| Food         | broccoli  | corn | lime |

