.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, baking
3 different games are played: go, scrabble, backgammon
1. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person playing go and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | baking | traveling |
| Game   | scrabble    | backgammon | go   |

