.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different games are played: poker, whist, bridge
House: palace, futuristic, art-deco
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing whist is between the person playing bridge and the futuristic house##2
3. the palace house is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Game      | bridge | whist   | poker |
| House   | art-deco  | palace | futuristic   |

 